        "row_DP3BFk": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4DB8F7F2-8453-4F48-AFEB-65F271FB36D3.jpg",
            "caption": "Traditional Craft · Restored by Hand",
            "heading": "The Art of Cane Chair Restoration",
            "text": "<p>Cane chair restoration is one of Britain's oldest craft traditions — and one that's nearly disappeared from the high street. Every seat is re-woven by hand, strand by strand, using the same techniques that have been used for centuries.</p><p>Whether your chair has a few broken strands or needs a full re-cane from scratch, the result is a seat that's as strong and beautiful as the day it was made. Properly restored cane can last decades with basic care.</p>",
            "button_label": "Get a quote",
            "button_link": "mailto:Charliebthomas@icloud.com?subject=Chair%20caning%20quote&body=Hi%20Charlie%2C%0A%0AI%27d%20like%20a%20quote%20for%20a%20chair.%0A%0A-%20Type%20of%20chair%3A%0A-%20What%20needs%20doing%3A%0A-%20Rough%20size%2Fpattern%3A%0A%0A(Please%20attach%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20seat%20and%20the%20whole%20chair.)%0A%0AThanks!"
          }
        },
        "row_6qgXj8": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/50B79282-B000-47C0-8E8E-33F13E84A9C8.jpg",
            "caption": "Honest Timelines · No Shortcuts",
            "heading": "What to Expect",
            "text": "<p>A full re-cane is not a quick job — and it shouldn't be. Each hole is threaded individually, with the weave checked and tensioned throughout to ensure an even, durable result.</p><p>Current turnaround is approximately 4 weeks from receipt of the chair. This reflects the time the work actually takes, not an arbitrary wait — and it means every chair gets the attention it deserves. You'll receive updates throughout the process.</p>",
            "button_label": "Get a quote",
            "button_link": "mailto:Charliebthomas@icloud.com?subject=Chair%20caning%20quote&body=Hi%20Charlie%2C%0A%0AI%27d%20like%20a%20quote%20for%20a%20chair.%0A%0A-%20Type%20of%20chair%3A%0A-%20What%20needs%20doing%3A%0A-%20Rough%20size%2Fpattern%3A%0A%0A(Please%20attach%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20seat%20and%20the%20whole%20chair.)%0A%0AThanks!"
          }
        },
        "row_mDhizy": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4D424418-011A-4C63-81C6-F4EA9C0120B2.jpg",
            "caption": "Transparent Pricing · No Surprises",
            "heading": "How Pricing Works",
            "text": "<p>Cane restoration is priced by complexity rather than by the hour — so you know what you're paying before any work begins. Prices start at £30 for small seats and £80 for larger, more intricate patterns.</p><p>To get an accurate quote, email a photo of the top and underside of your chair to Charliebthomas@icloud.com. Most quotes are returned within 48 hours. There's no obligation to proceed.</p>",
            "button_label": "Get a quote",
            "button_link": "mailto:Charliebthomas@icloud.com?subject=Chair%20caning%20quote&body=Hi%20Charlie%2C%0A%0AI%27d%20like%20a%20quote%20for%20a%20chair.%0A%0A-%20Type%20of%20chair%3A%0A-%20What%20needs%20doing%3A%0A-%20Rough%20size%2Fpattern%3A%0A%0A(Please%20attach%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20seat%20and%20the%20whole%20chair.)%0A%0AThanks!"
          }
        }
